{"id": 547, "genre": 1000, "title": "这些礼貌用语的意思已经变了", "description": "哎，这是一个称谓对方“X狗”“XX狗”象征情谊的年代。", "record_count": 6234, "comment_count": 40, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20160607194424m4sPLgtqGNxzU2J8.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 1, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2015-09-25T10:50:46Z", "questions": [{"id": 447, "title": "这些礼貌用语的意思已经变了", "content": "这些礼貌用语的意思已经变了", "genre": 2, "options": [{"id": 12455, "content": "晚安——我要去干别的了，拜拜了您嘞", "image": "img/option/option/2016060719331486aG7FwsuNZzJDdI.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 12456, "content": "再见——再也不想见到让我胸闷气短的你。", "image": "img/option/option/201606071933157ac3mYXkV0Wgvfln.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 12457, "content": "好的——我！才！不！想！听！你！的！", "image": "img/option/option/201606071933156AVRji8WcB3ytpOq.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 12458, "content": "对不起——我就知道你要说没关系。", "image": "img/option/option/20160607193315DezCdX7TocShHuxW.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 12459, "content": "久等了——我就是化妆耽误了一两小时而已。", "image": "img/option/option/20160607193316qGgRnYMZ5s6pmUoy.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 12460, "content": "实在过意不去——下回有事儿还找你。", "image": "img/option/option/2016060719331743k62cNzPhjefUH1.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 12461, "content": "甭客气——其实，是会感觉有那么一点点麻烦啦。", "image": "img/option/option/20160607193317of8LKvEuQysPtJAT.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 12462, "content": "回见——哟呵，一晃三年就过去了呢。", "image": "img/option/option/20160607193317Rz3K2utEYkwhMJDH.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}]}]}